Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.geolocation.geoip2

Class GeolocationServiceWithOverrides

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.geolocation.BaseGeolocationService
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.geolocation.geoip2.GeolocationServiceWithOverrides
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable, IGeolocationService
public class GeolocationServiceWithOverrides extends BaseGeolocationService implements IGeolocationService
A geolocation service that "wraps" another one. It is equiped with a set of rules, which override the resolution rules of the nested service when required.
Author:
nikolay.grozev
